{"tid":1374188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1974年可以成立廉政公署，2019年成立獨立調查委員會一樣得！","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:47:03.000Z","uid":266968,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8372156d07156d947f42d7908681a08b76cfa361","tid":1374188,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"1974年可以成立廉政公署脫離警方的獨立反貪污部門管制你班黑警<br />\n2019年要成立獨立調查委員會一樣得！<br />\n你班友越反抗，證明你地越身有屎！<br />\n係呀，話你呀望，屌你老母！黑警全家下地獄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/about/history/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fhistory%2Findex.html&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F13obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=0d86e4e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/about/history/index.html</a><br />\n以上網址是廉署誕生的經過 (文字版本)<br />\n大家覺唔覺得歷史過程與現狀對比熟口熟面?<br />\n下面節錄部份重點(黃字為現狀相似補充)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">市民飽受貪污<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">濫權暴力</span></span></strong></del>之苦</span></span></strong><br />\n六、七十年代，<br />\n貪污<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">濫權暴力</span></span></strong></del>風氣在警隊中更為嚴重。受賄的警務人員更包庇黃、賭、毒等各種非法罪行，社會治安、秩序受到嚴重的威脅。市民雖飽受貪污的禍害，卻敢怒而不敢言。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">社會風暴如箭在弦</span></span></strong><br />\n貪污<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">濫權暴力</span></span></strong></del>無疑已成為香港一個嚴重的社會問題，但是，當時政府對此卻似乎束手無策。普羅大眾對<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">濫權暴力</span></span></strong></del>貪風猖獗已達忍無可忍地步，愈來愈多市民就政府漠視此問題的態度公開表達他們的激憤。七十年代初期，社會上匯聚了一股強大的輿論壓力。公眾人士不斷向政府施壓，要求採取果斷行動，打擊貪污。最後，一名外籍總警司的貪污案，令民怨升達沸點，政府不得不立即採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一觸即發</span></span></strong><br />\n學生們在維多利亞公園舉行集會，抗議和批評政府未能恰當處理貪污問題，集會獲數以千計的群眾響應。市民又手持寫著「反貪污、捉葛柏」的橫額到街上示威，要求政府緝拿潛逃的葛柏歸案。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">果斷的決定</span></span></strong><br />\n麥理浩爵士說：「我認為有需要成立一個嶄新的機構，由德高望重的人員領導，以全力打擊<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">濫權暴力</span></span></strong></del>貪污，並且挽回公眾的信心。公眾對一個與任何政府部門，包括警務處，毫無連繫而完全獨立的組織明顯較具信心。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NQNbPOe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNQNbPOe.gif&h=5c358d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b645969f7190eaa2151b83233a8799bc40406bae","tid":1374188,"uid":266968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxowpot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpxowpot.jpg&h=8f7048fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c778eb0b27dd3f55f6fc2f5498ccbc2ab9fd5fa2","tid":1374188,"uid":266968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfCEBC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfCEBC8.png&h=92664954&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93766f0d0b62a1d4fe951bb9fc16bf9b61e94129","tid":1374188,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qr2QK9C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqr2QK9C.gif&h=935c4bc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfe18c63708ab51fd19a34281765d5e489e84f6d","tid":1374188,"uid":266968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9PPkgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9PPkgZ.jpg&h=ce568aa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f839324735facad4b48abf511391bd3553787af","tid":1374188,"uid":34334,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-